    "A primary concern is the preparedness of educators in this rapidly evolving AI landscape.",
    "Continuous and comprehensive training for teachers is crucial to ensure that they can effectively integrate AI tools into their pedagogical practices.",
    "Equally important are the ethical and social implications of AI in education.",
    "The integration of AI necessitates a critical approach to address biases, ensure privacy and security, and promote ethical use.",
    "Another significant hurdle is the accessibility of AI resources."
